title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 7PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 7PM” game were:
2-8-8-7
(two, eight, eight, seven)
